> bugs, read the dokan readme.txt

> according to dokan documentation, IsDirectory should
be set to TRUE by the fs programmer if one of the operations
CreateFile or {Create,Open}Directory acts on a directory
and IsDirectory is false. should check it back.
 
> fsync: isdatasync is always set to 0
> readdir: use getdir if no readdir function defined
> locking
> implement create
> use 64 bits off_t
